      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for a driver who values reliability over a flawless appearance. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small door dings consistent with its age, along with some minor paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and there are some persistent stains on the floor mats, though all gauges and electronics remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and handles well, having received regular oil changes, though it does have a minor oil seep common for its mileage. It is a solid, honest daily driver that will get you where you need to go without any major surprises.",
