    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings to ensure long-term structural and internal integrity. Suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein B16 adjustable dampers for improved turn-in response and lateral stability. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the chassis remains rigid and the compression across all cylinders is within factory tolerances. A purist\u2019s specification ready for spirited B-road touring",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
